        <title type="html"><![CDATA[耐心的说服教育，提高他们的科学文化水平]]></title>
        <id>https://hihaixiaodai.github.io/post/nai-xin-de-shuo-fu-jiao-yu-ti-gao-ta-men-de-ke-xue-wen-hua-shui-ping/</id>
